<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Deletion Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; text-align: center; margin:
      0; padding: 0; } .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 30px auto; background: white;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header {
      background-color: #b90000; color: white; padding: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
      .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; } .content { padding: 20px; text-align: left; } h2 {
      color: #333; } p { font-size: 16px; color: #555; } .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px;
      background: #0b1741; color: white; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; } a { color: #0b1741;
      font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; } .button { display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #0b1741; color: white; border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Account Deleted</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Goodbye, {{name}}!</h2>
        <p>
          We’re sorry to see you go. Your account associated with
          <strong>{{email}}</strong>
          has been successfully deleted from our system.
        </p>
        <p>
          If this was a mistake, or you change your mind, you can always create a new account by
          visiting our website:
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.iamabhi.tech" class="button">Create New Account</a>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out to us anytime at
          <a href="mailto:official@iamabhi.tech">official@iamabhi.tech</a>.
        </p>
        <p>Thank you for being a part of our community.</p>
        <p><strong>- Abhishek Kumar</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">&copy; 2025 Abhishek Kumar | All rights reserved</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>